---
/**
 * FAQ Component
 * Addresses common questions and objections using accordion format
 * Uses native <details>/<summary> for accessibility and zero-JS implementation
 * Philosophy: Clear, direct answers - no jargon, maintains emotional safety
 */
---

<section class="faq" aria-labelledby="faq-heading">
  <div class="container-text faq-content">
    <h2 id="faq-heading">Questions you might have</h2>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What does this cost?</summary>
        <p>We're not ready to discuss pricing yet. Join the waitlist to be notified when we launch.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How long does it take?</summary>
        <p>As long as you need. DraftOne works at your pace—not on a timeline.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Does AI write for me?</summary>
        <p>No. AI coaches—you write. Every word in your manuscript is yours.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Is my story private?</summary>
        <p>Yes. Your writing is fully private and belongs to you.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What do I need?</summary>
        <p>Just a browser. No special software or writing experience required.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>When will this launch?</summary>
        <p>We're building now. Join the waitlist for early access.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What if I'm not a good writer?</summary>
        <p>That's exactly who DraftOne is for. We help you build the skill as you write.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Section: vertical padding, no background (uses body bg) */
  .faq {
    padding-top: var(--space-10);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-10);
  }

  /* Content wrapper: horizontal padding */
  .faq-content {
    padding-left: var(--space-4);
    padding-right: var(--space-4);
  }

  /* Desktop spacing - more generous vertical padding */
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .faq {
      padding-top: var(--space-16);
      padding-bottom: var(--space-16);
    }

    .faq-content {
      padding-left: var(--space-6);
      padding-right: var(--space-6);
    }
  }

  /* Extra-large desktop - consistent with other sections */
  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .faq {
      padding-top: 9.375rem;    /* 150px */
      padding-bottom: 9.375rem; /* 150px */
    }
  }

  /* Headline: serif, left-aligned (different from centered sections) */
  .faq h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5); /* 40px gap to first FAQ item */
    text-align: left;
  }

  /* FAQ List: stack vertically */
  .faq-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2); /* 16px between items */
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .faq-list {
      gap: var(--space-3); /* 24px on desktop */
    }
  }

  /* FAQ Item: card-like appearance with border */
  .faq-item {
    background-color: var(--bg-elevated);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-4);
    transition: box-shadow var(--transition-base), border-color var(--transition-base);
  }

  .faq-item:hover {
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    border-color: var(--accent-secondary);
  }

  /* Open state: subtle emphasis */
  .faq-item[open] {
    border-color: var(--accent-primary);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .faq-item {
      padding: var(--space-4) var(--space-5);
    }
  }

  /* Summary (Question): bold, clickable, with custom marker */
  .faq-item summary {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    cursor: pointer;
    list-style: none; /* Remove default marker */
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    transition: color var(--transition-fast);
  }

  /* Remove default disclosure triangle across browsers */
  .faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  .faq-item summary::marker {
    display: none;
  }

  /* Hover state for summary */
  .faq-item summary:hover {
    color: var(--accent-primary);
  }

  /* Focus state for keyboard navigation */
  .faq-item summary:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid var(--accent-primary);
    outline-offset: 2px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  }

  /* Custom indicator (+ icon) */
  .faq-item summary::after {
    content: '+';
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transition: transform var(--transition-base);
  }

  /* Rotate indicator when open */
  .faq-item[open] summary::after {
    content: '−'; /* Minus sign when open */
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .faq-item summary {
      font-size: var(--text-lg); /* Slightly larger on desktop */
    }
  }

  /* Answer (Paragraph): revealed on expand */
  .faq-item p {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-top: var(--space-3); /* Gap from question */
    margin-bottom: 0;
    padding-left: 0; /* Left-aligned with question */
    max-width: none; /* Override default p max-width */
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .faq-item p {
      font-size: var(--text-lg);
      margin-top: var(--space-4); /* More space on desktop */
    }
  }

  /* Animation for content reveal */
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: no-preference) {
    .faq-item summary {
      transition: color var(--transition-fast);
    }

    .faq-item summary::after {
      transition: transform var(--transition-base);
    }
  }
</style>
